      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Pinterest – Workflow 1: Prepare Pins (runs weekly)\n\n**What it does:** finds newly Posted blogs, reads the blog page, pulls all content images, plans pins (1 carousel of 3 hero images + single pins for the rest, 3/month), AI writes title/description/alt, writes review rows to the **Pinterest Pins** tab.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Credentials: Google Sheets OAuth2 + OpenAI API key on the relevant nodes.\n2. Create tabs: **Pinterest Pins** and **Board Map** (Category → Pinterest Board).\n3. Add **Pinterest Status** column to Blogs.\n4. Check **Set Config** values.\n\n**Note:** the image-extraction selector (Extract & Plan) may need tuning to your live blog HTML.",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 420
